•How do I use Roid?
Copy all your ROMs files into a directory on your device and select it within Roid. This directory is allowed to have subdirectories. After the scan completes you should see your games.

•Why aren\'t my games detected?
If your games are compressed, try uncompressing them. If this doesn\'t work try putting ROMs into separate directories, one for each system with the following names: $SYSTEMS.
